  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ offers opportunity management for contacts (leads), customers, quotes, and appointments. Users can easily create quotes that can be printed, emailed, and converted into tickets.</p><p>A quote has all of the features of a standard ticket with a few key differences:</p><ul><li><p>Inventory is not pulled nor consumed for a quote.</p></li><li><p>Quotes are not included in revenue reports.</p></li><li><p>Quotes do not require a transaction to close out the ticket.</p></li></ul><p>Quotes also have workflows that follow the standard system you use for tickets and repairs. Converting a quote into an active ticket is a one-click process, and once converted, the related inventory is immediately pulled to the ticket.</p><h3 id=\"Quotes:CreateandViewaQuote-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934458927\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contacts Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246809\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2022080562\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes: Save a Ticket as a Quote</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934917634\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes: Convert a Quote to a Ticket</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934491696/Appointments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934491696\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Appointment Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246465\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notification Resources</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175256.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Quotes:CreateandViewaQuote-BuildaQuotefromtheOpportunitiesList\">Build a Quote from the Opportunities List</h2><p /><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Opportunities</strong> \u2192 <strong>Quotes</strong>. On the Quote Management screen, click the <strong>Add button</strong> on the right of the page and select the type of quote you would like to create: Quick Sale, Repair, or Trade-in.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175259.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175302.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"211\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175305.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Under the Customer &amp; Billing Agent section, add an existing customer to the quote using the <strong>Search Contact box</strong> or create a new lead by clicking the <strong>+New Contact button</strong>.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: Similar to a standard ticket, a customer must be attached to the ticket before you can save it.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175308.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>In the Ticket Items section of the ticket, add any products/services to the ticket, like the standard workflow.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: The Catalog Item status will show as pending since it is not removing any stock from your inventory.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175310.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Click an available Ticket Status Buttons at the bottom of the page to save your quote.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: Since a quote cannot accept payment, you can move it to Closed status at any point.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175316.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>(Optional) After saving the ticket, you are directed to the Ticket View page. You can use the Ticket Action Buttons to print the quote, or if you have set up <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246465\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notifications</a>, you can send it to the customer via email. The invoice will be noted as a quote.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175320.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175328.png?api=v2\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"Quotes:CreateandViewaQuote-ConvertaTicketintoaQuote\">Convert a Ticket into a Quote</h2><p>This feature must be activated by a Manager or a user with Admin privileges. For more information, see <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2022080562\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes: Save a Ticket as a Quote</a>.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: This option will only be possible when saving the ticket for the first time. If it has already been progressed to an existing status, this option will not be available.</p><p /><p>If you create a new ticket and would like to save it as a quote for your customer, you must have a customer and a repair device, item, or labor attached to the ticket. If the ticket meets these requirements, a new selection will appear at the bottom of the ticket, along with the standard ticket save statuses. Click <strong>Save as Quote</strong> to convert the ticket to a quote, which will be searchable in your Quote List and Ticket List (if filtered to include quotes).</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/Quote%2010.png?api=v2\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"Quotes:CreateandViewaQuote-ViewtheQuoteList\">View the Quote List</h2><p /><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Opportunities</strong> \u2192 <strong>Quotes</strong>. By default, any quote created within the last 90 days will show on this list. You can use the filters to sort for quotes with different parameters and use the Options button under the Actions column to view, edit, or convert the quote into a ticket.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175331.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934262304/image-20230622-175337.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.22.X</p>",
